Arrays in java:
Arrays allow us store multiple values in one variable.we use to indexes to get back the value.

Why we should learn Arrays:

if we have to store alot of values if becomes very hard to manage a lot of variables.

Syntax of Arrays:
we can create arrays in two different ways.
   Datatype[]arr={element 1,element2,element3};

   system.out.println(arr[1])

   second way of creating arrays:

   datatype[] arr=new datatype[size]

   note:
   other than using loops we can